<FILEID>AP-NR-06-14-88 0145EDT</FILEID>
<1ST_LINE>u a BC-ExecutionsList 1stAdd   06-14 1310</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>BC-Executions List, 1st Add,1361</2ND_LINE>
<HEAD>UNDATED: abusive mother.</HEAD>
<HEAD>1986</HEAD>
<TEXT>
   51. James Terry Roach, 25, electrocuted in South Carolina on
Jan. 10 for murdering two teen-agers when he was 17 years old.
Accomplice Joseph Carl Shaw was executed Jan. 11, 1985.
   52. Charles Bass, 29, executed by injection in Texas on March 12
for murdering a Houston city marshal during a shootout.
   53. Arthur Lee Jones Jr., 47, electrocuted in Alabama on March
21 for murdering a cab driver during a robbery.
   54. Daniel Morris Thomas, 37, electrocuted in Florida on April
15 for murdering a white man and raping his wife during a 10-month
crime spree that officials said was racially motivated. Thomas was
black.
   55. Jeffery Allen Barney, 28, executed by injection in Texas on
April 1, for raping and murdering the wife of a minister who had
befriended him.
   56. David Livingston Funchess, 39, executed in Florida's
electric chair on April 22 for fatally stabbing two people in 1974
during a holdup at the bar where he had been fired.
   57. Jay Kelly Pinkerton, 24, executed by injection in Texas on
May 15 for fatally stabbing two women.
   58. Ronald J. Straight, 42, executed in Florida's electric chair
on May 20 for the 1976 death of a businessman. (execution No. 30,
Timothy Palmes, involved same killing).
   59. Rudy Ramos Esquivel, 50, executed in Texas by injection on
June 9 for murdering a narcotics officer.
   60. Kenneth Albert Brock, 37, executed in Texas by injection on
June 19 for shooting to death a convenience store manager during a
robbery.
   61. Jerome Bowden, 33, electrocuted in Georgia on June 24. The
mentally retarded man had killed a woman during a robbery, and the
execution drew protests from rock stars and associations of
retarded citizens.
   62. Michael Marnell Smith, 40, electrocuted in Virginia on July
31 for raping and killing a woman.
   63. Randy Lynn Woolls, 36, executed by injection in Texas on
Aug. 20 for beating, slashing and burning a drive-in movie cashier.
   64. Larry Smith, 30, executed by injection in Texas on Aug. 22
for shooting a convenience store clerk in a robbery that netted $25.
   65. Chester Lee Wicker, 37, executed by injection in Texas on
Aug. 26 for kidnapping a woman and killing her by burying her alive
on a beach.
   66. John William Rook, 27, executed by injection in in North
Carolina, Sept. 19 for raping, knifing and running over a nurse,
leaving her to die.
   67. Michael Wayne Evans, 30, executed by injection in Texas on
Dec. 4 for murdering a church pianist who was shot and slashed to
death as she prayed to God to forgive her.
   68. Richard Andrade, 25, executed by injection in Texas on Dec.
18 for the rape-murder of a woman who was stabbed at least 14 times
and left in a pool of blood.
</TEXT>
<HEAD>1987</HEAD>
<TEXT>
   69. Ramon Hernandez, 44, executed by injection in Texas on Jan.
30 for the 1980 shooting death of a mechanic during a burglary at a
closed service station.
   70. Eliseo Moreno, 27, executed by injection in Texas on March 4
for the 1983 shooting death of a state trooper while on a 160-mile
