ticket. It compels, I think, a real undeniably generic Southerner.''
   Did he have anyone in particular in mind to fill the post?
   ``Yeah, lots,'' said Babbitt, who proceeded to reel off a list
of possibilities that included Sen. Albert Gore of Tennessee,
presidential hopeful Jesse Jackson, Sen. Dale Bumpers of Arkansas,
Florida Sen. Bob Graham, and Sen. Lloyd Bentsen of Texas.
