<DATELINE>PHOENIX, Ariz. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Democrat Dave Moss announced Tuesday he
will seek his party's nomination for congressional seat held by
Republican Bob Stump.
   Moss, 64, a former candidate for governor, condemned what he
